data.description:
Free rent for December (Valid from 12/15/2023 till 12/31/2023)

Beautiful 3 bed and 2 bath farm house on 4.4 acres of picturesque land. The updated kitchen features granite countertops and enough storage. A large 2 room workshop provides additional space for storage or can keep large equipment. Gated pastures with water access are perfect for livestock whether you have goats, chickens, or other animals. It includes 2 barn, chicken coops and 2 ponds. A 2-car carport offers convenience and protects your vehicles. This house is located in the highly sought-after Princeton ISD ensures access to excellent schools. Includes refrigerator and washer/dryer. The home is available now.

Tenant will pay all utilities including propane
